videoSnippet.title: He Who Lives By The Sword, Dies By The Sword | WRC2017 | Round 10
videoSnippet.description:

The "King Salman World Blitz & Rapid Championships 2017" in Riyadh from Decemer 26th to 30th. The first five rounds of the rapid tournament take place on December 26th. A record $2 million prize fund has attracted most of the world's best players.

Baadur Jobava vs Shakhriyar Mamedyarov
World Rapid Championship (2017), Riyadh KSA, rd 10, Dec-27 
Trompowsky Attack: General (A45)

1. d4 Nf6 2. Bg5 Ne4 3. Bf4 d5 4. f3 Nd6 5. Nc3 e6 6. e3 Be7 7. Qd2 Nd7 8. O-O-O O-O 9. Kb1 c6 10. Bd3 b5 11. Bd6 Bd6 12. f4 b4 13. Nce2 c5 14. dc5 Nc5 15. Nf3 a5 16. Ned4 a4 17. h4 Ba6 18. g4 Qb6 19. Ka1 Bd3 20. cd3 Nb3 21. Nb3 ab3 22. a3 ba3 23. Kb1 Bb4 24. Qe2 ab2 25. Qb2 Ra2 26. Qb3 Ra3 27. Qb2 Rb8 28. Rc1 Qa6 29. Rc7
